  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Dig Dug II is a 1985 action video game developed and published by Namco for Japanese arcades. It is a sequel to 1982's Dig Dug. Pookas and fire-breathing Fygars return as the enemies, but the side view tunneling of the original is replaced with an overhead view of an island maze.",
